Class VeluxDiscoveryService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.smarthome.config.discovery.AbstractDiscoveryService

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @NonNullByDefault
public class VeluxDiscoveryService
extends org.eclipse.smarthome.config.discovery.AbstractDiscoveryService
implements java.lang.Runnable
    The VeluxDiscoveryService is responsible for discovering actuators and scenes on the current Velux Bridge.
